Line3.7FA05: Very different from him, fortunately. Tyrael set off before Elias did. I don’t know what drew him away, but I could tell he was...afraid. We fell apart after he left.
Line1.7FA05: Us three Horadrim—Elias, Lorath, myself—and an angel, Tyrael.
MenuLabel: “How many people lived here in its heyday?”
